{"tid":1813222,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角偽黃甜品鋪督灰起咗手足底","createTime":"2020-01-06T06:13:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T13:08:49.000Z","uid":317818,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c14a9a3c0f7d817474c48ed368d99afea0f4501d","tid":1813222,"uid":317818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dKLRAr1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdKLRAr1.png&h=14e7d846&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9kNTOM2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kNTOM2.png&h=522844fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rsuKVr4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrsuKVr4.png&h=0644f3f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n事源係呢間偽黃甜品鋪 <br />\n因為有曬證據比黃藍店地圖admin<br />\n被黃藍店地圖官方認證為藍店<br />\n其後此偽黃老細為挽回黃店一名<br />\n因而斷估告密者為前同事<br />\n並在其公司FB上督灰抹黑該名前同事<br />\n你不滿成為藍店就搵前同事開刀<br />\n你有證據咪報返去比admin做返黃店囉<br />\n反正你個人本身就係偽黃為生意先做埋曬啲小動作<br />\n<br />\n一路聲稱同路人和理非 <br />\n郤並無對手足有提供任何回饋援助<br />\n無去過遊行 無過捐錢 郤一直騎劫和理非一名稱<br />\n試圖博取同情 繼續扮黃<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵制偽黃店</span>"},{"pid":"98cf85c148a77f3f10ad81bbe63afd4b264e3f48","tid":1813222,"uid":102700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:16:02.000Z","msg":"今日做乜咁多偽黃post"},{"pid":"dbe957d85a7f99d74d855e92bae6a9fd78128deb","tid":1813222,"uid":18552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:16:25.000Z","msg":"好仆街"},{"pid":"f4083944c184de5fb72e182927bb9ae2b1594e04","tid":1813222,"uid":431,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:24:08.000Z","msg":"服用雙飛人作興奮用途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75954747ebe52c5bd425ef15be0fa718c5627c08","tid":1813222,"uid":317818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T06:26:19.000Z","msg":"搞到我嗰前同事出街都擔心受怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/d